                <h1>How to Print Background Color in Microsoft Word</h1>
                <p>To print a background color in Word, first, ensure your document is set to print with colors. Go to "Design," then "Page Color," and choose your desired color. Before printing, access "File," select "Print," and ensure that "Print Background Colors and Images" is checked in the settings. Then, print your document, and the background color will appear!</p>
